grade_evaluation.et:
Grade A ("excellent"): student has participated in at least 7 seminars and all discussions and completed all tasks very well on time;
Grade B ("very good"): student has participated in at least 5 seminars and all discussions and completed all tasks well on time;
Grade C ("good"): student has participated in less than 5 seminars and 2 discussions but completed all tasks;
Grade F ("failed"): poor participation and not completed tasks.
